These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, handball, cycling, snowboarding
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, domino, canasta
1. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of techno##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person who's sport is handball is the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
6. the person playing domino is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Sport   | snowboarding | handball | cycling | surfing |
| Game     | canasta  | mah-jongg       | bridge    | domino     |

