.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, disco, d&b, country
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, montecristo, fonseca, chaman
1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the fan of country is between the owner of the frog and the game-smoker##2
6. the chaman-smoker is between the fan of country and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the fan of disco is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the fan of d&b is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep      | disco  | country  | d&b |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Cigar         | montecristo    | chaman | fonseca | game |

