.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, 7up, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, skiing, climbing, handball
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the paramedic is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the lawyer is the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the person drinking coffee is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is handball##2
9. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person drinking 7up and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage        | iced-tea | 7up     | coffee   | soy-milk     |
| Sport       | skiing   | parkour   | climbing | handball |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

