.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, skateboard, snowmobile, ship
There 4 different types of food: tomato, asparagus, kiwi, pumpkin
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person eating asparagus is on the far right##1
 2. the person eating pumpkin is the person driving the train##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating pumpkin is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person eating asparagus is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 9. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is between the owner of the bird and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Transport           | train  | ship | skateboard     | snowmobile |
| Food   | pumpkin | tomato  | kiwi | asparagus       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

