The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, iced-tea, coffee
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 8. the lawyer is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person drinking coffee and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday          | may         | february         | november     | january      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate     | iced-tea       | coffee | water |

