6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre           | spy | thriller | adventure  | comedy |
