 7. the argentine is the swisher-smoker##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing whist##1
10. the dutch is the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
