 4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 7. the person eating papaya is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is the indonesian##1
